  "description": "This dataset investigates the neural mechanisms underlying anticipatory attention and expectation through electroencephalography (EEG). It contains raw EEG data from an experimental paradigm designed to dissociate anticipatory processes related to attention versus expectation, providing insights into how the brain prepares for upcoming events based on different cognitive states. This dataset is mirrored on NEMAR from OpenNeuro (ds004502).",
